commit.message:
More user-friendly docs inside Vidify

Work towards #94, replacing texts with what are considered more
user-friendly and understandable ones overall.

Mpv correctly freezes finished videos

Using 'keep-open' with 'always' instead of as an option (I don't
actually know what value it took being an option...) fixes #101.

Removing the option completely also fixes #101, but the videos wouldn't
be frozen in place after finishing, which would cause issues with the
default video for errors.
